text: Teruchiyo Takamiya (born 18 February 1942) is a Japanese equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
